- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a novel estimator that uses bidirectional LSTMs to learn temporal dependencies. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with spoken dialogue systems. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the paper aims to improve user satisfaction in dialogue systems.
